cd path/to/your/project
git init
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/portfolio-site.git
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git push -u origin master
2. Rename index.html if needed
Make sure your main file is named index.html and is in the root of the repo (not inside a folder).

3. Enable GitHub Pages
Go to your repo on GitHub

Click Settings → Scroll to Pages (on the left menu)

Under Source, choose main (or master) branch and root folder

Click Save

